subject: College Athletics
Softball
lead_paragraph: Christina Enea had a run-scoring single and Kim Waleszonia scored on an error in the first inning for Florida, which defeated second-seeded U.C.L.A., 2-0, in the Women’s College World Series in Oklahoma City.
